185typedef struct
186{
187 union
188 {
189 volatile uint32_t cfg;
190
191 struct
192 {
193 uint32_t uFuncSel : 4; // [3:0]
194 uint32_t eGPInput : 1; // [4:4]
195 uint32_t eGPRdZero : 1; // [5:5]
196 uint32_t eIntDir : 2; // [7:6]
197 uint32_t eGPOutCfg : 2; // [9:8]
198 uint32_t eDriveStrength : 3; // [12:10] // See information and details above
199 uint32_t ePullup : 3; // [15:13]
200 uint32_t uNCE : 5; // [20:16]
201 uint32_t uRsvd_0 : 1; // [21:21]
202 uint32_t eCEpol : 1; // [22:22]
203 uint32_t eTimerSel : 1; // [23:23]
204 uint32_t uRsvd_1 : 1; // [24:24]
205 uint32_t ePowerSw : 1; // [25:25] // Select pads only, otherwise reserved
206 uint32_t eForceInputEn : 1; // [26:26]
207 uint32_t eForceOutputEn : 1; // [27:27]
208 uint32_t eDeeperSleepCfg : 3; // [30:28]
209 uint32_t uRsvd_2 : 1; // [31:31]
210 } cfg_b;
211 } GP;
212} am_hal_gpio_pincfg_t;

804#define AM_HAL_MASK32(n) ((uint32_t)1 << ((n) & 0x1F))
805
806#define AM_HAL_GPIO_RDn(pin) ((volatile uint32_t *)&GPIO->RD0 + (((pin) >> 5) & 0x7))
807#define AM_HAL_GPIO_WTn(pin) ((volatile uint32_t *)&GPIO->WT0 + (((pin) >> 5) & 0x7))
808#define AM_HAL_GPIO_WTCn(pin) ((volatile uint32_t *)&GPIO->WTC0 + (((pin) >> 5) & 0x7))
809#define AM_HAL_GPIO_WTSn(pin) ((volatile uint32_t *)&GPIO->WTS0 + (((pin) >> 5) & 0x7))
810#define AM_HAL_GPIO_ENn(pin) ((volatile uint32_t *)&GPIO->EN0 + (((pin) >> 5) & 0x7))
811#define AM_HAL_GPIO_ENCn(pin) ((volatile uint32_t *)&GPIO->ENC0 + (((pin) >> 5) & 0x7))
812#define AM_HAL_GPIO_ENSn(pin) ((volatile uint32_t *)&GPIO->ENS0 + (((pin) >> 5) & 0x7))
814
815//*****************************************************************************
816//
838//
839//*****************************************************************************
840#define am_hal_gpio_input_read(n) ((*AM_HAL_GPIO_RDn((n)) >> ((n) % 32)) & 1)
841#define am_hal_gpio_output_read(n) ((*AM_HAL_GPIO_WTn((n)) >> ((n) % 32)) & 1)
842#define am_hal_gpio_enable_read(n) ((*AM_HAL_GPIO_ENn((n)) >> ((n) % 32)) & 1)
843
844//*****************************************************************************
845//
877//*****************************************************************************
878#define am_hal_gpio_output_clear(n) (*AM_HAL_GPIO_WTCn((n)) = AM_HAL_MASK32(n))
879#define am_hal_gpio_output_set(n) (*AM_HAL_GPIO_WTSn((n)) = AM_HAL_MASK32(n))
880#define am_hal_gpio_output_toggle(n) \
881 if ( 1 ) \
882 { \
883 AM_CRITICAL_BEGIN \
884 (*AM_HAL_GPIO_WTn((n)) ^= AM_HAL_MASK32(n)); \
885 AM_CRITICAL_END \
886 }
887
888#define am_hal_gpio_output_tristate_output_dis(n) (*AM_HAL_GPIO_ENCn((n)) = AM_HAL_MASK32(n))
889#define am_hal_gpio_output_tristate_output_en(n) (*AM_HAL_GPIO_ENSn((n)) = AM_HAL_MASK32(n))
890#define am_hal_gpio_output_tristate_output_tog(n) \
891 if ( 1 ) \
892 { \
893 AM_CRITICAL_BEGIN \
894 (*AM_HAL_GPIO_ENn((n)) ^= AM_HAL_MASK32(n)); \
895 AM_CRITICAL_END \
896 }
